## 🚀 How to Run This Project

```bash
git clone https://github.com/asra-here/finance-tracker-app.git
cd finance-tracker-app
flutter pub get
flutter run
```

---

## 🔒 Firebase Integration

The app is Firebase-ready but not configured. To activate:
- Add your Firebase project
- Use `google-services.json` in `android/app/`
- Set up authentication and Firestore

